36:55.579 --> 37:01.726
An intermediate, glorious heaven, then an ultimate new heaven, new earth, and new Jerusalem, new city.

37:02.828 --> 37:03.488
Do you see it?

37:05.230 --> 37:06.532
Does it change how you live?

37:08.414 --> 37:09.155
That's the point.

37:09.335 --> 37:19.026
Titus chapter 2, verse 11 to 14 says, for the grace of God has appeared, we're really arrived, bringing salvation for all people, training us,

37:19.138 --> 37:39.224
to renounce on godliness and worldly passions, to live self-controlled upright and godly lives in his present age, waiting for our blessed hope, and the appearing of our glory of our great God and Savior, Jesus Christ, who gave himself for us to redeem us from all lawlessness, and to purify for himself a people for his own possession, who are zealous for good works.

37:39.684 --> 37:44.210
All of this is to change our lives, how we look, how we live.

37:48.322 --> 37:50.205
Now let me close with a sports illustration.

37:52.648 --> 37:54.531
All right, I'm talking to Red Sox Nation, right?

37:58.277 --> 38:01.081
What event changed everything for Red Sox fans?

38:01.141 --> 38:01.662
What event?

38:01.882 --> 38:02.383
Do you remember?

38:03.825 --> 38:04.286
What was that?

38:07.791 --> 38:09.293
It was the reversing of the curse.

38:10.855 --> 38:11.937
Have you ever heard about the curse?

38:13.359 --> 38:14.280
You're familiar with that?

38:15.082 --> 38:18.066
Babe Ruth was sold to the New York Yankees for how much, do you remember?

38:18.722 --> 38:19.964
$100,000.

38:21.587 --> 38:23.129
Back then, it's a lot of money, huh?

38:23.149 --> 38:23.970
It's a lot of money today.

38:24.691 --> 38:35.008
So he sold to the New York Yankees and ever since then, the Boston Red Sox, who were one of the top contenders in baseball, never could win a championship.

38:38.633 --> 38:41.257
I remember in 1985, you won't ever forget this.

38:41.698 --> 38:43.461
They were getting pretty close in the World Series.

38:43.501 --> 38:44.543
I think it was Game 6.

38:45.484 --> 38:46.706
First baseman was who?

38:48.834 --> 38:50.637
Wow, a little lesson here.

38:50.837 --> 38:51.418
Bill Buckner.

38:52.219 --> 38:53.461
And the balls hit the Bill Buckner.

38:53.481 --> 38:59.870
And I remember where I was when Bill Buckner allowed the ball to go right between his legs.

38:59.890 --> 39:01.372
I was at Liberty, I was in college.

39:02.233 --> 39:04.957
We didn't have TVs in our room, so we had to go to a rec room.

39:06.159 --> 39:10.846
And I watched Bill Buckner miss that very easy, easy play.

39:12.068 --> 39:13.650
And the Red Sox lost again.

39:16.130 --> 39:21.395
But in 2004, they were down three to zero against two, the Ankeys.

39:24.338 --> 39:29.002
And then they won four straight, and the curse was reversed.

39:32.485 --> 39:39.072
The curse of sin in Eden is reversed in heaven, the new heavens, the new earth, the new Jerusalem.

39:40.012 --> 39:45.938
And this should affect us as Christians even more than the reversing of the curse,

39:46.018 --> 39:47.319
of the Boston Red Sox.

39:51.224 --> 39:54.908
I want you to take the best, the best of what we have now.

39:55.709 --> 40:00.474
And in these places called the New Heaven and New Earth, it's so much better.

40:02.936 --> 40:03.757
Here's an image here.

40:03.817 --> 40:06.881
On the left here, think of the steak dinner.

40:06.961 --> 40:07.722
It's awesome.

40:10.425 --> 40:12.487
But think of a meal that's even better.

40:12.527 --> 40:15.410
It's perfect steak.

40:16.482 --> 40:17.885
Perfect asparagus.

40:20.049 --> 40:21.792
Perfect food that's nutritious.

40:25.038 --> 40:26.180
Think about our bodies.

40:27.503 --> 40:30.308
This is a picture of Neil Gorman, Neil Gorman in heaven one day.

40:30.649 --> 40:31.390
That's going to be Neil.

40:34.937 --> 40:37.842
The Bible says that we're going to experience all of these things.

40:40.578 --> 40:51.035
Some think that in heaven and new heavens and new earth, we're about the age of our prime, which is around 30 years old, that everybody's going to look about that age, about 30 or so.

40:52.577 --> 40:53.258
I don't doubt that.

41:01.391 --> 41:08.242
A good and beautiful future doesn't mean that we're inactive and just hang out until the sweet chariot from by on by comes and picks us up.

41:09.666 --> 41:11.188
We're about to be the father's business.

41:11.469 --> 41:12.430
This is what we're supposed to do.

41:12.831 --> 41:14.914
Be about the father's business until he comes.

41:16.577 --> 41:18.941
Or you're taken and you go there.

41:20.824 --> 41:23.708
Can I just say to you as your pastor, new pastor, just don't hang out.

41:24.249 --> 41:24.730
Lend a hand.

41:26.854 --> 41:27.815
Lend a hand, do something.

41:28.716 --> 41:32.983
If this is cross-way Milford to you, then serve somewhere.

41:33.444 --> 41:34.466
We have team cross-way.

41:35.147 --> 41:37.170
Plenty of options over there for you to plug in.

41:37.890 --> 41:39.913
After the service, you don't even pray about it.

41:39.933 --> 41:40.935
You don't have to fast about it.

41:41.095 --> 41:42.036
You don't have to call your lawyer.

41:43.879 --> 41:47.285
Just simply do something and sign up over there.

41:48.527 --> 41:50.730
We have connections that's coming up next week.

41:51.171 --> 41:53.594
It's a great little meeting that's going to happen right here after the service.

41:53.635 --> 41:57.701
Just to make contact with the leaders, learn a little bit about Crossway Milford.

42:01.086 --> 42:03.570
If you're new, since we moved into this facility,

42:04.002 --> 42:06.706
I would encourage you to wait after service next week, right around here.

42:07.007 --> 42:09.290
And we'll have a great little meeting together, about 15 minutes.

42:09.310 --> 42:09.771
It'll be fun.

42:13.556 --> 42:15.960
And we have Monday school starting with Pastor Dave Ripper.

42:16.441 --> 42:17.783
I'm excited for Dave to come up here.

42:19.606 --> 42:20.247
Can we bring that up?

42:20.307 --> 42:22.450
Is there a QR code for that?

42:22.490 --> 42:23.191
Nothing?

42:23.251 --> 42:24.052
I don't have that up there?

42:25.254 --> 42:25.895
Sign up for that.

42:26.656 --> 42:28.299
I think we have 25 people or so.

42:29.521 --> 42:33.106
Let's get at least 30 in there to learn the Bible and how to read the Bible.

42:34.338 --> 42:34.939
I read the book.

42:34.999 --> 42:35.780
It's fantastic.

42:35.800 --> 42:37.502
I told Dave that it blessed me.

42:37.522 --> 42:40.926
I had tears in my eyes as I was reading that book.

42:40.946 --> 42:42.008
Monday school will bless you.

42:42.909 --> 42:43.510
It will bless you.

42:44.411 --> 42:47.335
People need forgiveness and freedom, closing thoughts.

42:47.815 --> 42:50.198
They need a new future, a good and beautiful one.

42:51.981 --> 43:02.514
They need to be in heaven with us, the new heavens and the new earth, a sin-free environment, a magnificent city,

43:03.298 --> 43:09.485
a beautiful city, and God is going to use cross-way milfer to populate heaven.

43:12.628 --> 43:13.209
Do you believe this?

43:14.750 --> 43:16.092
Father, we thank you for your word.

43:16.132 --> 43:20.416
The afterlife is just spectacular.

43:21.498 --> 43:26.183
Help us to keep our eyes on things above, not on things on the earth.

43:27.544 --> 43:30.607
What you have provided, we will enjoy and we'll give you glory.

43:31.548 --> 43:33.170
But may we be so

43:33.282 --> 43:37.147
so vertical, not as much horizontal.

43:38.509 --> 43:42.474
And so the afterlife you have prepared, and it's going to be incredible.

43:46.098 --> 43:47.440
Pray for your arrival, Jesus.

43:47.480 --> 43:48.101
You said, come.

43:49.062 --> 43:49.563
You're coming.

43:49.623 --> 43:50.163
You're coming.

43:50.464 --> 43:51.585
Please come, Lord Jesus.

43:53.608 --> 43:57.733
If there's someone sitting here that hasn't accepted Jesus as their Savior, please do that today.

43:59.936 --> 44:01.618
Please do that before He comes back.

44:03.906 --> 44:04.927
We thank you for your word.

44:04.947 --> 44:07.771
We thank you for this series on heaven.

44:10.454 --> 44:11.215
In Jesus' name.

44:12.236 --> 44:16.280
Amen.

44:16.300 --> 44:20.205
Thanks for listening to the Crossway Christian Church's Middleford campus sermon podcast.

44:20.505 --> 44:27.754
If you like to plug into the life of our community or have any questions that we might be able to answer, visit our website at crosswayscc.org to connect with us.

44:28.214 --> 44:29.496
Until next time, we can be with you.

44:29.776 --> 44:31.378
May the Lord bless you and keep you.

